1038
01:50:09,990 --> 01:50:12,930
-Sir?  -That's right.

1039
01:50:22,500 --> 01:50:26,840
-What were their names?  -Irwin Wade and Adrian Caparzo.

1040
01:50:29,010 --> 01:50:30,530
Wade and?

1041
01:50:31,850 --> 01:50:33,580
Caparzo.

1042
